<title>USA: American Safety Razor promotes CFO.</title>
<headline>American Safety Razor promotes CFO.</headline>
<dateline>VERONA, Va. 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>American Safety Razor said on Wednesday that it promoted Thomas Kasvin to senior vice president administration, chief financial officer.</p>
<p>Kasvin's previous title was vice president, chief financial officer, a company spokesman said.</p>
<p>Kasvin will continue to be responsible for the company's human resource department and its financial and accounting functions.</p>
